precis:
ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE TRANSFER OF OFFENDERS ACT which adds
eleven countries to the list of countries with whom Canada has a bilateral
or multilateral treaty that allows people convicted of an offence in a
foreign country to serve their sentence in their native country.
